Subject: Squash
data: 1 Dipika Pallikal and Joshna Chinappa created history by winning the first-ever gold medal in which of the following games in the 20th Commonwealth Games recently? A Table Tennis B Squash C Badminton D Netball Answer: Option [B]
2 Name the player who became the first Indian to reach semifinals of World Junior Squash in Namibia? A Tushar Kothari B Kush Kumar C Shashi Pandey D Javed Mohammad Answer: Option [B]

3 Who amongst the following have emerged as the man and the woman squash champions after winning the respective finals of the National Squash? A Saurav Ghosal and Joshna Chinappa B Saurav Ghosal and Anaka Alannkamony C Harinder Sandhu and Joshna Chinappa D None of these Answer: Option [A]
4 Where is the Headquarters of World Squash Federation located? A Hastings B New Delhi C Madrid D Berlin Answer: Option [A]
5 Where is the headquarters of Squash Rackets Federation of India located? A New Delhi B Bhupal C Chennai D Jaipur Answer: Option [C]
